// Home Screen Home Welcome to your Todo App “The secret of getting ahead is getting started.” In this app, you can: - Add new tasks to keep track of your to-do list.
- View all your tasks in one place.
- Edit and update your tasks as needed.
- Delete tasks that are no longer needed. Getting Started: 1. Use the navigation bar at the bottom to access different sections of the application.
2. To view all tasks, go to the 'Tasks' section.
3. To add a new task, use the floating action button in the 'Tasks' section.
4. To edit or delete a task, go to the 'Tasks' section and select the task you want to modify.
